    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a \"period\" of doubt. it feels permanent. like the core of me is just... hollow. i look at people living these normal, mundane lives and i can't even understand how they do it. if i'm not creating, if i don't have that purpose, then what's actually the point of the breathing and the eating and the just... existing? it feels like i'm just playing a part in a play that's already ended.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
